<p><span style="font-size: 20px;"><span><strong>1.西瓜</strong></span></span><span style="font-size: 20px;"><span><strong>视频（平挂）</strong></span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 20px;"><span><strong>2.腾讯</strong></span></span><span style="font-size: 20px;"><span><strong>now直播（55%）</strong></span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 20px;"><span><strong>3.快</strong></span></span><span style="font-size: 20px;"><span><strong>手（平挂）</strong></span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 20px;"><span><strong>4.抖</strong></span></span><span style="font-size: 20px;"><span><strong>音</strong></span></span><span style="font-size: 20px;"><span><strong>（平</strong></span></span><strong>挂）</strong></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 20px;"><span><strong>5.腾讯直</strong></span></span><span style="font-size: 20px;"><span><strong>播（招募商家入驻）</strong></span></span></p>
